### Config Loading - Test Endpoints

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Health Check (shows environment)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Send Email (shows SMTP config from YAML)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "user@example.com",
  "subject": "Config-Driven Email",
  "body": "This email uses SMTP settings from config.yaml!"
}

### 3. Get Counter Value (shows counter seed from YAML)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/counter/value

### 4. Increment Counter (seed starts at 200 from config)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/counter/increment

### 5. Log Message (shows logger config from YAML)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/log
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Testing config-driven logger"
}

### 6. Test with different environments
# Set environment variables before running:
# $env:LOG_LEVEL="debug"
# $env:COUNTER_SEED="5000"
# $env:APP_ENV="production"
# Then restart the server and test again

